1. *Vodi* ga u šetnju. (Take him for a walk.)
2. Ona je *vodila* decu u školu. (She was taking the children to school.)
3. On je *vodio* konja. (He was leading the horse.)
4. Ona je *vodila* čas. (She was teaching the class.)
5. On je *vodio* sebe. (He was leading himself.)
6. Ona je *vodila* diskusiju. (She was leading the discussion.)
7. Ona je *vodila* računa o sebi. (She was taking care of herself.)
8. On je *vodio* pregovore. (He was negotiating.)